<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 16 Jul 2026 05:59:04 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a587324e63e9</link><description>&lt;p&gt;继续练习HTML/CSS，这次制作一个带右侧边栏的布局。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Bare-bones webpage with a header, main content area, sidebar with an author bio, and a footer" height="1688" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/spencerdub/6a587324e63e9.png" width="2552"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://spencerdub.some.pics"&gt;@spencerdub&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Jul 2026 05:59:04 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>单列页面布局练习</title><link>https://some.pics/6a5872d2a3e7a</link><description>&lt;p&gt;HTML和CSS练习：制作一列页面布局&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Plain HTML page displaying placeholder text in a one-column layout" height="1430" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/spencerdub/6a5872d2a3e7a.png" width="1542"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://spencerdub.some.pics"&gt;@spencerdub&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Jul 2026 05:57:41 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a57def86f2c7</link><description>&lt;p&gt;抱歉，我们已经打烊了。营业中，请进。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="White storefront on a street corner with white iron bars on all of the windows and the front door. Everything is weathered. There is one sign in the window that reads “sorry, we’re closed,” and a second in an adjacent window that reads “open, come in.” There are wig busts in the window with various head wraps on them. A sign painted on the concrete at the entryway reads “national shirt shops coast to coast.”" height="1704" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/markwyner/6a57def86f2c7.jpg" width="2272"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://markwyner.some.pics"&gt;@markwyner&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Jul 2026 19:26:51 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a57ddbbe4596</link><description>&lt;p&gt;位于图森市中心的芝加哥音乐商店。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Front of a music store in an old brick and concrete building, painted dark red. The sign on the building reads “new and used pianos and organs,” with a decorative letter “c” at the edge where store’s name begins. There are many stacked drum sets in the windows with many sale signs." height="1704" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/markwyner/6a57ddbbe4596.jpg" width="2272"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://markwyner.some.pics"&gt;@markwyner&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Jul 2026 19:21:35 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a57d2c420fea</link><description>&lt;p&gt;被囚禁的&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A close-up black and white photograph captures a toucan with its large, distinctive beak." height="1600" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/cliff538/6a57d2c420fea.jpg" width="2400"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://cliff538.some.pics"&gt;@cliff538&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Jul 2026 18:34:47 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>